<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HAI SINTA & SYIFA - Sistem Layanan Terpadu Farmasi RSUD Sinjai</title>
    
    <!-- Google Fonts & Font Awesome Icons -->
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    
    <!-- Integrasi Leaflet JS & CSS untuk Real OSM Map -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.css" integrity="sha256-p4NxAoJBhIIN+hmNHrzRCf9tD/miZyoHS5obTRR9BMY=" crossorigin="" />
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/leaflet@1.9.4/dist/leaflet.js" integrity="sha256-20nQCchB9co0qIjJZRGuk2/Z9VM+kNiyxNV1lvTlZBo=" crossorigin=""></script>
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-soft-blue: #38bdf8;
            --primary-deep-blue: #0284c7;
            --accent-magenta: #f472b6;
            --accent-cyan: #22d3ee;
            --dark-bg: #030712;
            --dark-card: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.45);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --glass-shadow: 0 16px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            --text-light: #f8fafc;
            --text-gray: #94a3b8;
            --transition-smooth: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1);
            --font-family: 'Plus Jakarta Sans', 'Inter', sans-serif;
            --success-color: #10b981;
            --danger-color: #f43f5e;
            --warning-color: #fbbf24;
        }

        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: var(--font-family);
        }

        body {
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, #0c152b 0%, #030712 100%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: var(--text-light);
            min-height: 100vh;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Ambient Glowing Background Blobs */
        body::before, body::after {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            filter: blur(140px);
            z-index: -1;
            opacity: 0.15;
            animation: float-blobs 20s infinite alternate;
        }

        body::before {
            width: 500px;
            height: 500px;
            background: var(--primary-soft-blue);
            top: -10%;
            left: -10%;
        }

        body::after {
            width: 600px;
            height: 600px;
            background: var(--accent-magenta);
            bottom: -10%;
            right: -10%;
            animation-delay: -10s;
        }

        @keyframes float-blobs {
            0% { transform: translate(0, 0) scale(1); }
            100% { transform: translate(100px, 50px) scale(1.2); }
        }

        @keyframes pulse-ring {
            0% { transform: scale(0.6); opacity: 0; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { transform: scale(1.5); opacity: 0; }
        }

        @keyframes map-radar {
            0% { opacity: 0.15; }
            100% { opacity: 0.35; }
        }

        .glass-panel {
            background: var(--dark-card);
            backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(25px);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--glass-shadow);
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }

        .glass-panel:hover {
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            box-shadow: 0 16px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .form-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 4px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .form-label {
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary-soft-blue);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.6px;
        }

        .form-control {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 10px 14px;
            color: #fff;
            outline: none;
            font-size: 13px;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            width: 100%;
        }

        .form-control:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary-soft-blue);
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.55);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 12.5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            border: none;
        }

        .btn-glass {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            color: var(--text-light);
        }

        .btn-glass:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-soft-blue), var(--primary-deep-blue));
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.25);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-danger {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--danger-color), #b91c1c);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.25);
        }

        .btn-danger:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-warning {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--warning-color), #d97706);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.25);
        }

        .btn-warning:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 16px rgba(251, 191, 36, 0.4);
        }

        .navigation-row {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            white-space: nowrap;
            padding-bottom: 4px;
            scrollbar-width: none;
        }
        .navigation-row::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }

        .nav-group-container {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            padding: 3px 6px;
            border-radius: 12px;
        }

        .nav-group-label {
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 800;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            color: var(--text-gray);
            padding: 0 6px;
            border-right: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        }

        .nav-tab {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
            font-size: 11.5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            background: transparent;
        }

        .nav-tab:hover, .nav-tab.active {
            color: #fff;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-color: var(--glass-border);
        }

        .nav-tab.active {
            border-color: var(--primary-soft-blue);
            box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.15);
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.04);
        }

        .chat-list-item.sla-critical {
            border-left: 3px solid var(--danger-color);
            background: rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.06) !important;
            animation: pulse-danger-light 2s infinite alternate;
        }

        @keyframes pulse-danger-light {
            0% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 4px rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.08); }
            100% { box-shadow: inset 0 0 12px rgba(244, 63, 94, 0.25); }
        }

        .drug-article-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 16px;
            transition: var(--transition-smooth);
        }
        .drug-article-card:hover {
            border-color: var(--primary-soft-blue);
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.03);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
        }

        .db-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            font-size: 9px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }
        .db-badge-local {
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.12);
            color: var(--primary-soft-blue);
            border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
        }

        .map-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            height: 220px;
            background: #090f1d;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.25);
            box-shadow: inset 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), 0 0 15px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.1);
        }

        .drug-tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
            padding: 3px 8px;
            background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
            color: var(--primary-soft-blue);
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 11px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    
    <!-- Custom Dialog Overlay -->
    <div id="custom-dialog-overlay" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/85 backdrop-blur-md z-[11000] items-center justify-center p-4">
        <div class="glass-panel max-w-[400px] w-full p-6 text-center">
            <div id="dialog-icon" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl"></div>
            <h3 id="dialog-title" class="text-white text-base font-bold mb-1.5">Notifikasi</h3>
            <p id="dialog-message" class="text-xs text-[#94a3b8] mb-5 leading-relaxed"></p>
            <div id="dialog-actions" class="flex gap-2.5 justify-center">
                <button id="dialog-btn-cancel" class="btn btn-glass hidden flex-1 py-2">Batal</button>
                <button id="dialog-btn-confirm" class="btn btn-primary flex-[1.5] py-2">Lanjutkan</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Duration Simulation Dialog -->
    <div id="duration-simulation-overlay" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/90 backdrop-blur-md z-[11500] items-center justify-center p-4">
        <div class="glass-panel max-w-[360px] w-full p-6 text-center border-cyan-500/25">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4 text-xl">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-truck-ramp-box animate-pulse"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-sm font-extrabold mb-2 text-center">Simulasi Durasi Pengantaran</h3>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-slate-300 mb-5 leading-relaxed">
                Tentukan waktu pengiriman aktual kurir untuk evaluasi target ketepatan waktu pelayanan (SLA 20 Menit):
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-2.5">
                <button onclick="submitDurationSimulationResult(15)" class="btn btn-primary w-full py-2.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-teal-600 border-none font-bold text-xs">
                    Cepat (15 Menit - Sesuai Target)
                </button>
                <button onclick="submitDurationSimulationResult(25)" class="btn btn-danger w-full py-2.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-rose-500 to-red-600 border-none font-bold text-xs">
                    Terlambat (25 Menit - Melebihi Target)
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- ONBOARDING OVERLAY POPUP -->
    <div id="onboarding-overlay" class="fixed inset-0 bg-black/95 backdrop-blur-lg z-[10000] flex items-center justify-center p-4">
        <div class="glass-panel max-w-[420px] w-full p-6 text-center relative overflow-hidden border-sky-400/20">
            <div class="absolute -top-12 -right-12 w-32 h-32 bg-sky-500/10 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
            
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-pink-500 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl mx-auto mb-4 shadow-md shadow-sky-500/20">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-hospital-user"></i>
            </div>
            
            <h2 class="text-sm font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white mb-1 uppercase">SELAMAT DATANG DI PORTAL LAYANAN TERPADU RSUD SINJAI</h2>
            <p class="text-[10px] text-cyan-400 font-bold tracking-widest uppercase mb-3">SINTA & SYIFA ON CARE</p>
            
            <p class="text-[11px] text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed text-justify mb-4 p-3 bg-white/5 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
                Demi kelancaran komunikasi, harap simpan nomor WhatsApp resmi apotek RSUD Sinjai sebagai syarat administrasi utama dalam pengantaran resep dan pengaktifan pengingat obat harian Anda.
            </p>

            <!-- Save Official Pharmacy Contact First -->
            <button class="btn btn-warning w-full py-2.5 text-[11px] mb-4 font-bold flex justify-center items-center gap-1.5" onclick="generatePharmacistOfficialVCard()">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-address-book"></i> (Simpan Nomor WA Apoteker)
            </button>

            <div class="border-t border-white/5 pt-4 text-left">
                <div class="form-group mb-3">
                    <label class="form-label text-cyan-400 block mb-1">daftarkan nomor whatsapp anda disini: <span class="text-rose-500">*</span></label>
                    <input type="text" id="onboard-wa-input" class="form-control text-sm tracking-wide font-bold py-2.5 text-center" placeholder="Contoh: 08135xxxxxxxxxx" onkeypress="handleOnboardKeyPress(event)">
                </div>
                <button class="btn btn-primary w-full py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-sky-400 to-sky-600 font-extrabold text-white tracking-wide text-xs" onclick="submitOnboardingAccess()">
                    MASUK PORTAL SEKARANG <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-right text-[9px]"></i>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Auth Modal (Internal Staf) -->
    <div id="auth-modal-overlay" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/80 backdrop-blur-md z-[10500] items-center justify-center p-4">
        <div class="glass-panel max-w-[360px] w-full p-6 text-left">
            <h3 class="text-white text-base font-bold mb-1.5"><i class="fa-solid fa-lock text-[#f472b6] mr-1.5"></i> Akses Staf Apotek</h3>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-[#94a3b8] mb-4 leading-relaxed">Masukkan kode sandi otorisasi apoteker RSUD Sinjai untuk mengawasi status pelayanan.</p>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label class="form-label">Sandi Otoritas</label>
                <input type="password" id="auth-password" class="form-control" placeholder="••••••••" onkeypress="handleAuthKeyPress(event)">
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-2 mt-4">
                <button class="btn btn-glass flex-1 py-2 text-xs" onclick="closeAuthModal()">Batal</button>
                <button class="btn btn-primary flex-[1.5] py-2 text-xs" onclick="submitAuthInternal()">Buka Dasbor</button>
            </div>
            <p class="text-[9px] text-center text-[#94a3b8] mt-3 bg-white/5 py-1 rounded-lg border border-white/5">
                Sandi Apoteker Jaga: <code class="text-amber-300">sinta2026</code>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- QR Handshake Modal -->
    <div id="qr-handshake-overlay" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/85 backdrop-blur-md z-[10800] items-center justify-center p-4">
        <div class="glass-panel max-w-[360px] w-full p-6 text-center">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-400 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-lg">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-qrcode"></i>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-white text-sm font-bold mb-1">VCard Kontak Pasien</h3>
            <p class="text-[11px] text-[#94a3b8] mb-4">Pindai kode QR dengan kamera HP petugas apotek untuk mempermudah penyimpanan kontak otomatis pasien baru.</p>
            
            <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded-xl inline-block mb-4 shadow-md">
                <img id="qr-code-img" class="w-40 h-40" src="https://placehold.co/160x160/ffffff/000000?text=SINTA+PATIENT+QR" alt="Contact QR Code">
            </div>

            <div class="text-[11px] bg-white/5 border border-white/5 p-2.5 rounded-xl mb-4 text-left">
                <strong class="text-amber-400 block mb-0.5" id="qr-patient-name">Nama Pasien</strong>
                <span class="text-slate-300 block text-[10px]" id="qr-patient-wa">WhatsApp: -</span>
            </div>

            <button class="btn btn-glass w-full py-2 text-xs" onclick="closeQrHandshakeModal()">Tutup Pratinjau</button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="app-container" class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
        
        <!-- HEADER NAVIGASI PREMIUM -->
        <header id="top-header" class="bg-black/85 backdrop-blur-lg border-b border-white/5 sticky top-0 z-[1000] px-4 py-3">
            <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-stretch md:items-center gap-3">
                
                <!-- Logo & Brand Info -->
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-400 to-pink-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center text-white text-base shadow-md shadow-sky-500/20">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-house-medical-flag"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                            <h1 class="text-base font-extrabold tracking-tight bg-gradient-to-r from-white to-sky-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">HAI SINTA & SYIFA</h1>
                            <span id="db-status-pill" class="db-badge db-badge-local">Layanan Aktif</span>
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-[9px] text-[#22d3ee] font-bold uppercase tracking-wider" id="portal-role-label">Sistem Edukasi & Pengantaran Obat RSUD Sinjai</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Profile Context -->
                <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-3">
                    <div class="text-right hidden sm:block">
                        <strong class="text-xs text-white block" id="profile-name">Pengunjung Umum</strong>
                        <span class="text-[9px] text-cyan-400 font-medium" id="profile-sub">Akses Pasien</span>
                    </div>
                    <button id="admin-gate-btn" class="btn btn-glass px-3 py-1.5 text-[10.5px] border-cyan-500/10 text-cyan-400" onclick="handlePortalSwitchClick()">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-lock"></i> Portal Staf
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Horizontal Tab Navigation Row (Anti-Hamburger) -->
            <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto mt-2.5 overflow-x-auto">
                <nav class="navigation-row py-0.5" id="top-nav-menu-bar">
                    <!-- Nav tabs dynamically inserted via JavaScript -->
                </nav>
            </div>
        </header>

        <!-- MAIN VIEWPORT CONTENT -->
        <main id="main-view" class="flex-grow px-4 py-6 max-w-[1200px] w-full mx-auto">
            <div class="border-l-4 border-sky-400 pl-3 mb-6 flex justify-between items-center">
                <div>
                    <h2 id="module-title" class="text-xl font-extrabold text-white tracking-tight">Memuat Modul...</h2>
                    <p id="module-subtitle" class="text-[11px] text-[#94a3b8] mt-0.5">Detail informasi.</p>
                </div>
                <!-- Mini Hour Operational Status Info -->
                <div id="service-status-header-badge" class="px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-[10px] font-bold bg-emerald-500/10 text-emerald-400 border border-emerald-500/20">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-store"></i> Pelayanan Buka
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- MODULE 1: PUBLIC REGISTRATION & DIRECT SERVICES -->
            <div id="pub-beranda-module" class="module-content-panel hidden">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
                    <div class="lg:col-span-2 glass-panel p-5 flex flex-col justify-between bg-gradient-to-br from-white/[0.01] to-transparent">
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-[9px] font-extrabold text-[#22d3ee] uppercase tracking-wider block mb-1">ASISTEN FARMASI DIGITAL RSUD SINJAI</span>
                            <h3 class="text-lg font-extrabold text-white mb-2">Edukasi Obat SINTA & Layanan SYIFA On Care</h3>
                            <p class="text-xs text-[#94a3b8] leading-relaxed text-justify">
                                Portal informasi kefarmasian terintegrasi RSUD Sinjai. Kami melayani penjelasan aturan pakai obat secara personal, pengingat minum obat terjadwal secara proaktif, serta pengantaran resep aman langsung ke depan pintu rumah Anda di wilayah Sinjai (SLA Target 20 Menit).
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mt-4 text-[10px] text-sky-400 bg-sky-950/30 border border-sky-500/20 py-2 px-3 rounded-lg">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button text-xs text-emerald-400"></i>
                            <span>Nomor WhatsApp Aktif Anda: <strong class="text-white font-mono" id="display-active-wa">-</strong></span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="glass-panel p-5 flex flex-col justify-between border-cyan-500/10">
                        <div>
                            <span class="text-[9px] font-extrabold text-cyan-400 uppercase tracking-widest block mb-2">Status Pelayanan</span>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs mb-2">
                                <span class="text-slate-400">Sistem SINTA &amp; SYIFA:</span>
                                <span id="service-status-pill" class="text-emerald-400 font-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle text-[6px] mr-1 animate-pulse"></i> Online</span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex justify-between items-center text-xs">
                                <span class="text-slate-400">Apoteker Jaga:</span>
                                <span class="text-cyan-400 font-bold"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-md text-[10px] mr-1"></i> Standby</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-[10px] text-center bg-black/40 py-1.5 px-2 rounded-lg text-slate-300 font-semibold" id="live-wita-timer">
                            00:00:00 WITA
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- MAIN FORMULIR LAYANAN TERPADU -->
                <div class="glass-panel p-5" id="p-reg-form-panel">
                    <h3 class="text-white text-sm font-extrabold mb-1 flex items-center gap-1.5"><i class="fa-solid fa-file-medical text-sky-400"></i> Formulir Pelayanan SINTA &amp; SYIFA</h3>
                    <p class="text-[11px] text-[#94a3b8] mb-4">Lengkapi sisa kolom di bawah ini untuk mengaktifkan pengantaran obat ke rumah sekaligus pengawasan obat oleh asisten SINTA.</p>
                    
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
